Do not delete. -->\n                        </div>\n\n                        <h2 class=\"masthead twenty-margin center\">A Help Desk Designed To Save You Time</h2>\n                        <h5 class=\"center\">Rhino Support helps you provide better, faster support.</h5>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"six columns\">\n                            <p class=\"large\">We get it.  We're a software company and we know what it's like to get tickets from customers on a regular basis.  We also know the importance of being able to respond to customers in a timely fashion.</p>\n                            <p class=\"large\">That's why Rhino Support helpdesk software was designed to make the process of providing world-class support, drop-dead easy.   It's fast, efficient and really easy to use.</p>\n                            <p class=\"large\"><a href=\"#pricing\" class=\"scrolling\">Set up your account</a> and try it out for 15 days (on us)... or read below for a quick overview.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"six columns\">\n                            <a href=\"/Templates/3.0/screenshots/full-homepage.png\" class=\"fancybox\"><img src=\"/Templates/3.0/screenshots/screen-homepage.png\" alt=\"Help Desk Software, Open Tickets\"></a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    \n                    <hr class=\"dashed\">\n\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"six columns\">\n                            <h3><br>One-Click Ticket Management</h3>\n                            <p>We pay attention to every click because we know when you're dealing with hundreds of tickets, every one counts.</p>\n                            <p>Managing tickets with Rhino Support is fast, efficient and easy to use (for both you and your team). From the main control panel you'll be able to:\n                            </p><ul class=\"pretty\">\n                                <li>View the ticket message by hovering over the subject.</li>\n                                <li>Quickly assign tickets to a user or department.</li>\n                                <li>View tickets by creation date or last activity.</li>\n                                <li>Mark as important, delete and so much more.</li>\n                            </ul>\n                            <p></p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"six columns\">\n                            <a href=\"/Templates/3.0/screenshots/full-messagepreview.png\" class=\"fancybox\"><img src=\"/Templates/3.0/screenshots/screen-hoverdetail.png\" alt=\"Helpdesk, Message Preview\"></a>\n\n                            <div class=\"caption negativemargin\">View tickets directly from your dashboard.</div>\n                            <a href=\"/Templates/3.0/screenshots/full-department.png\" class=\"fancybox\"><img src=\"/Templates/3.0/screenshots/screen-assigndetail.png\" alt=\"Helpdesk, Assigned Preview\"></a>\n\n                            <div class=\"caption negativemargin\">Quickly assign tickets without viewing full ticket.</div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <hr class=\"dashed\">\n\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"six columns\">\n                            <h3>Set Up in Just a Few Minutes</h3>\n                            <p>There is no complicated \"install\" and you don't need a special server to use Rhino Support. It's a web-based solution that can be quickly integrated into your existing business a variety of ways.</p>\n                            <p>Our setup wizard will walk you through the essentials so that you can get started right away. Then if you want to incorporate some other \"bells and whistles,\" you can.</p>\n                            <h5>Within a few minutes you'll be able to:</h5>\n<ul class=\"pretty\">\n<li>Add new support agents.</li>\n<li>Create new departments.</li>\n<li>Update company information.</li>\n<li>Display a floating \"Support\" tab to your site and more!</li>\n</ul>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"six columns\">\n                            <a href=\"/Templates/3.0/screenshots/full-signup.png\" class=\"fancybox\"><img src=\"/Templates/3.0/screenshots/screen-setup.png\" alt=\"Live Chat Software, Setup Form\"></a>\n\n                            <div class=\"caption negativemargin\">Just fill in the blanks and the setup wizard will do the rest!</div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    \n\n                    \n                    <hr class=\"dashed\">\n\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"six columns\">\n                            <h3>Streamlined Features</h3>\n                            <p>The focus of Rhino is to create a great experience for you and your customers.
